title: #126 - Chris D'Elia
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we are joined once again by friend of the show, comedian Chris D'Elia! Together we discuss beef with Albuquerque, Cameo, throwing up in your mouth, frosted glass toilet stalls, having enough money to retire, and TikTok divorce cringe!
